<a href="<get-var base />.txt"><get-var desc />Source in text format</a> 
(requires
<a href="$(ROOT)/open-source/projects/XML-Grammar/Fiction/">XML-Grammar-Fiction’s</a> Screenplay-Text processing, in order to render)
<restore base desc />
</define-tag>

